config BR2_PACKAGE_FPGA_LED
	bool "fpga-led"
	help
	  User-space application that controls FPGA LEDs on the DE10-Nano
	  board via the UIO (Userspace I/O) driver.

	  The application maps the LED PIO peripheral registers through
	  /dev/uioX and cycles through LED patterns.

	  https://github.com/bleviet/cvsoc
